snippet.title: Official Godzilla: Strike Zone (iOS / Android) Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Godzilla: Strike Zone by Warner Bros. (iOS / Android)

Join a squadron of military heroes on a dangerous mission to face the ultimate force of nature: GODZILLA.

Experience the breathtaking high-altitude sky jump from the movie as you air-drop into a devastated San Francisco and embark on a series of first-person rescue missions to evacuate survivors before it's too late.

Your courage has never been more needed than it is today.

See GODZILLA in theaters May 16.

iTunes Store Page:

https://itunes.apple.com/app/com.wb.godzilla.strikezone/id855556927

Google Play:

https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.wb.goog.godzilla.strikezone
